headline: Delisting of Securities of Vicinity Motor Corp.; Bright Green Corporation; Smart for Life, Inc.; Focus Impact Acquisition Corp.; Cactus Acquisition Corp. 1; AltEnergy Acquisition Corp.; Lilium N.V.; APx Acquisition Corp.  I; Integral Acquisition Corporation 1; New Providence Acquisition Corp. II from The Nasdaq Stock Market
summary: NEW YORK, March 12, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- The Nasdaq Stock Market announced today that it will delist the common stock of Vicinity Motor Corp. Vicinity Motor Corp.’s stock was suspended on October 31, 2024 and has not traded on Nasdaq since that time. Nasdaq also announced today that it will delist the common stock of Bright Green Corporation.
